title: Miss U
lyrics:
Lyric Milena - Miss U

[Romanization]

I just wanna love you more
jom deo algo sipeojyeo
neoreul hyanghan maeum gamchul suga eomneunggeol

Every time I want you more
nega bogo sipeojyeo
jakkuman du nuneul ttel su eopge hae

Staying in my memories
uri durui Melody
nae ane sumgyeonwatdeon iyagireul moaseo

Tell me that you need me babe
malhaejullae Call my name
deo yonggireul nae dagaga bolkka

I miss you, miss you, miss you
I love you, love you
gyeote isseojwo

Oh for you, for you
dugeunggeorineun maeum
nan neoui pume anggigo sipeo

Can't stop thinking 'bout you even in my dreams
nae modeun nareun eoneusae neoro gadeukhae

Every time I want you more
jogeumeun duryeowodo
ijeneun soljikhi gobaekharyeo hae

Staying in my memories
uri durui Melody
nae ane sumgyeonwatdeon iyagireul moaseo

Tell me that you need me babe
malhaejullae Call my name
deo yonggireul nae dagaga bolkka

I miss you, miss you, miss you
I love you, love you
gyeote isseojwo

Oh for you, for you
dugeunggeorineun maeum
nan neoui pume anggigo sipeo

Please tell me that I’m in your heart
josimseure geonnen mal
neoreul joahae You know oh

난 너의 품에 안기고 싶어

너를 좋아해 You know oh
